  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A pilot prospective cohort study assessing the clinical utility of MRI evaluation of graft
      steatosis prior to transplantation will be conducted. An MRI of the donor liver within the
      transport cooler will be obtained on its way to the operating room.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The images from MRI will be analyzed to obtain information of fat content in all eight
      segments of the liver. Demographic, intra-operative, and post-operative patient data will be
      collected for each imaged graft.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
